ark_pagel-jennifer_jacquet-john_brockman-information" class="title">Information Gardens</a></div><div class="author"><a href="/memberbio/brian_eno" class="title"><span class="author">Brian&nbsp;Eno</span></a>,&nbsp;<a href="/memberbio/hans_ulrich_obrist" class="title"><span class="author">Hans Ulrich&nbsp;Obrist</span></a>,&nbsp;<a href="/memberbio/mark_pagel" class="title"><span class="author">Mark&nbsp;Pagel</span></a>,&nbsp;<a href="/memberbio/jennifer_jacquet" class="title"><span class="author">Jennifer&nbsp;Jacquet</span></a>,&nbsp;<a href="/memberbio/john_brockman" class="title"><span class="author">John&nbsp;Brockman</span></a><span class="date"> [ 10.16.11 ] </span></li><li class="related-conversation"><div class="title"><a href="/conversation/brian_eno-a-big-theory-of-culture" class="title">A Big Theory Of Culture</a></div><div class="author"><span class="byline">A Talk With&nbsp;</span><a href="/memberbio/brian_eno" class="title"><span class="author">Brian&nbsp;Eno</span></a><span class="date"> [ 3.31.97 ] </span></li></ul>  </div>
